Package utility.state

Class Phase

java.lang.Object
utility.state.Phase
Direct Known Subclasses:
Edit, ExecuteOrder, GameOver, IssueOrder, Reinforcement, Startup
public abstract class Phase extends Object
The phase class is an abstract class which has all the methods representing the commands in the game. There are different phases in the game which will be extending the methods of phase class. The relevant phase will have the implementation of methods according to its phase.
